  .row
    .span12.center{:style => "margin-top: 600px;"}
      %h1
        What do we do
  .row.vertical-spacing
    .span4.bigicon
      %i.icon-rocket.blue-icon
    .span4.bigicon
      %i.icon-road.blue-icon
    .span4.bigicon
      %i.icon-heart.blue-icon
  .row.center
    .span4
      %h2
        Inspire
    .span4
      %h2
        Connect
    .span4
      %h2
        Care
  .row.center
    .span4
      It is our mission to inspire students to discover and pursue their passion. Unlocking the full potential of students by create a healthy community to stimulate the sharing of knowledge.
    .span4
      Students can search and enroll for challenges that meet their interests. It is a unique opportunity for students to work with some of the leaders in the field.
    .span4
      Learn, share, make friends and have fun! That is our core value, we try to remove all obstacles to make it as accessible and enjoyable as possible for students to discover their passion.
